%% Ch01 Diagram 02 — Pask Conversation Loop (Pangaro)
%% Source: "intelligence emerges when systems learn to understand each other's understanding"
flowchart LR
    A["Agent A<br/>mental model"]
    B["Agent B<br/>mental model"]
    MA["A's model of B"]
    MB["B's model of A"]

    A -->|expresses| B
    B -->|expresses| A
    A --> MB
    B --> MA
    MA -->|refines| A
    MB -->|refines| B

    U((Shared<br/>understanding))
    MA -.-> U
    MB -.-> U
    U -.->|feedback| A
    U -.->|feedback| B
